CBRE are delighted to present, for lease, Units 3-4, 42 Keilor Park Drive, Keilor East.

This brand-new showroom/warehouse is strategically located along Keilor Park Drive and within 600m* of the Western Ring Road and 800m* of the Calder Freeway interchanges, providing excellent access to all major road arterial and the Melbourne Airport (4.5km*).

Key features include:
+ Total building area: 407sqm*
+ Ground floor showroom/warehouse: 311sqm*
+ First floor office: 96sqm*
+ High quality fixtures and fittings used throughout
+ 1 x Container height airport style glass door
+ 7m internal springing height
+ LED lighting 
+ Full amenities including lunchroom with kitchenette and male and female bathrooms plus shower
+ 8 exclusive car spaces on Title
+ Available for occupancy/inspection
+ Restricted Retail Permit

Please contact CBRE for an inspection and further information.

*approximate

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: EXCITING NEW SHOWROOM ON MAIN ROAD

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is delighted to present, for lease, 53 Slater Parade, Keilor East.

This is an outstanding opportunity to lease a warehouse space, enviously positioned within the highly sought after industrial precinct of Keilor East. 

This immaculate office/warehouse facility is located just off Keilor Park Drive and offers great access to the Western Ring Road and all other major arterials of the north and western suburbs.

Key features include:
+ Total building area: 344sqm*
+ IN1Z (Industrial Zone 1)
+ 5 on-site car spaces
+ Great access to Ring Road
+ Container height roller doors
+ Full staff amenities
+ Lockable security gates

Please contact CBRE to arrange an inspection or further information.

*approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: PRIME POSITION AND READY TO GO

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer for lease 1/22 Disney Avenue, Keilor East. This is a rare opportunity to acquire your own piece of this tightly held northern industrial market!

The subject property is strategically located in the heart of Keilor East offering good proximity to major arterials including the Metropolitan Ring Road, Tullamarine Freeway & Calder Freeway, furthermore only minutes from Melbourne Airport.

This multi-functional warehouse affords the following features;

+ Total building area of 343sqm*
+ Office/Reception area of 60sqm*
+ 4 Allocated car spaces
+ Container height roller door w/ container access
+ Two level office & reception area
+ Updated staff amenities 
+ Three phase power
+ Great proximity to major arterials
+ Rear private court yard 60sqm*
+ Mezzanine space with pallet access 60sqm* 
+ Great signage exposure along Western Ring Road

*approx.

+ Industrial 1 Zone (IN1Z)
